description:
Gia Jordan has been a porn star her entire adult life.
This has caused a mixing of her work life and private
life, they are now one. She truly is a nympho, she
truly is a slut, and she will be the first to tell you
so. Gia NEEDS sex daily-everything about her just
oozes sex. We paired her with Sgt Major, who hates
shooting with “porny” girls just like Gia. However
near the end of the first scene, the porn girl stops
“acting” and starts reacting. The fresh and
challenging situation takes her out of her element and
soon we have a normal girl suffering to get though a
Hogtied shoot. The concept is just beautiful in it’s
subtlety, if you know how to look.
title: Gia Jordan
